http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Bank-staff-hold-demonstration/article14619928.ece

The officials and staff of various banks under the banner of United Forum of Bank Unions staged a demonstration in front of the Canara Bank branch on the Mohanur road in the town on Thursday evening in support of the nationwide strike on Friday to protest against the unilateral amendments in labour laws. The agitation was led by V.Krishnasamy of Namakkal district unit of Bank Employees Association.L. Venkatasubramani, convener of Forum of Bank Unions, spoke.